      "raw_text": "Employment agents have protest\ned against Patrolman Daniels, who\nyesterday afternoon ordered ]. w.\nBilly, clerk for Switzer & Adams\nemployment agency. away from in\nfront of the Macho agency at 214\nStevens ST. Macho complained to\nthe officers that Billy was soliciting\nhis business.\n\n\nMacho. notorious In police circles\nfor the number of complaints made\nagainst him, will be hailed before\nthe city council Tuesday night in\nall probability to make a fight to\nretain his license. Mayor Moore,\nChief Rice and License Inspector\nGwydir have all recommended that\nhis license be revoked. 1t Is claim\ned that Macho has secured pledges\nfrom certain councilmen to oppose\nthe revocation. He certainly ap.\npears TO be exceedingly popular\nwith them, otherwise he would\nhave lost his license long ago."
